{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"23075-kasalina-ali-mu-ggulu","title":"Kasalina ali mu Ggulu","description":"Kate Namatovu yali bubi. Awulira obukoowu ne enyike. Yandikoze atye?  'Kulongoosebwa bwongo.' Omusawo bwe yagamba. Olowooza kate yaba atya? ","language":"Luganda","langCode":"lg","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Wambi Cornelius"],"illustrators":["Rodney Kawaayi"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/23075-kasalina-ali-mu-ggulu"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51015/size3/8ca3c666e0db264094f35933099a3709.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51015/size6/8ca3c666e0db264094f35933099a3709.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/50977/size6/609ccf50b208cceca649dd2b33ddea7f.jpg","text":"Kasalina alina oguntuntu mu mutwe.\nBanagujjamu batya?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/50978/size6/a0c61ebeb245521681ef916a46dd629f.jpg","text":"Gumukooya. Gumuluma. Gumuzitoya.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/50979/size6/15ef0703989779ddfab58d77ccb8378a.jpg","text":"Talya. \nTanywa. \nTeyeyagala nga edda.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/50985/size6/ca1c1fcf4c18e714ecf570c35e5d21ec.jpg","text":"Omusawo amusikaaninga omutwe.\nAlabye mwana watu.\nMukazi watu omutwe gutundujja.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51003/size6/e218a66686d10692fb4004e6983619e9.jpg","text":"Omusawo alabye ekitole mu mutwe.\nOmusawo agamba,\"kino ekitole kya\nmusaayi.\"\nTulina okukijja mu mutwe gwo kati.\"\nTulina ku kijjamu kati. Omusawo bwagamba bwatyo.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51004/size6/f524f7668c1245e218a6357806d5c892.jpg","text":"Baleeta ekitanda.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51005/size6/469a501e1ded69bb6ebbad2fdc727c8d.jpg","text":"Bategeka ebiso.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51006/size6/3ad7b3b50ee2b703e9ea3e0ee1995219.jpg","text":"Bamufumita empiso.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51007/size6/c600f21c76d308e87f57b472a2947bcd.jpg","text":"Basala omutwe gwa Kasalina.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51008/size6/b03e3c72d339557681c20ac4eb00adee.jpg","text":"Bajjamuo bwongo.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51009/size6/d1cb8585d6f0bebbc499337238af7f43.jpg","text":"Basalamu ekitole kyo omusaayi\nKasalina alinga mwana muto.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51010/size6/71fec655d08236024cca901149c7c788.jpg","text":"Obwongo babumuuzaamu\nOmutwe bagutunga","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51011/size6/c9a45a9172b497d6820d070ddf41e9fc.jpg","text":"Kasalina awulira byona bye bakola?\nNedda! Kasalina ali mu ggulu.\nTawulira. Talya. Talowooza.\nOkumala saawa nga 24.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51012/size6/5b9d725cea7b74c675bf9b0a6e2252f2.jpg","text":"Naalyoka adda engulu!","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51013/size6/a83213da4ba867e887cc520d46a4432e.jpg","text":"Kati ali bulungi.\nKati ayogera kaati.\nNga akaana akato.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/51014/size6/f379ddea0283ebcacf368ee187598c06.jpg","text":"Ffeena tusanyuka\nOlwa mukwano gwaffe\nKasalina eyalegga ku ggulu.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":110}}